## 辅助栈遍历

其实二叉树遍历这里，辅助栈遍历才是重点！！！

### 前序遍历

```Java
/**
 * 辅助栈前序遍历
 *
 * @param root
 */
public static void preOrderTraversalWithStack(TreeNode root) {
    if (root == null) {
        return;
    }
    Stack<TreeNode> stack = new Stack<>();
    TreeNode p = root;
    while (p != null || !stack.isEmpty()) {
        while (p != null) {
            System.out.print(p.data + " ");
            stack.push(p);
            p = p.leftChild;
        }
        if (!stack.isEmpty()) {
            p = stack.pop();
            p = p.rightChild;
        }
    }
}
